column5: Come stay on your own private floor in this amazing two-story home, with a gourmet kitchen, hardwood floors, two living rooms, (upstairs and downstairs), and a beautiful backyard with a sunny private patio! You'll be 20 minutes to downtown, and close to Lake Travis, at this impeccably clean and charming cottage, complete with adorable cat!
column8: private floor in central, charming Austin cottage!
